The "free" (advertising-rich) hosting things are not places
I go, and I read my e-mail in plaintext only, so please don't
go the Yahoo route or anything where the bells and whistles
outnumber the bytes of actual content.  I don't make the
rounds of blogs / websites, either -- mailing lists are
God's gift.

I'm good for $100, and it won't be the first time.

